### 2. 📥 Missing Body Parsing & Input Validation
There's no body parser middleware or input validation. If you add POST/PUT routes, raw unvalidated input is a major injection risk.

```js
app.use(express.json({ limit: '10kb' })); // Limit payload size to prevent DoS
app.use(express.urlencoded({ extended: false }));
