Abrupt process exits can corrupt in-flight requests or database writes.

```js
const server = app.listen(3000, () => {
  console.log('Server running on port 3000');
});

process.on('SIGTERM', () => {
  server.close(() => {
    console.log('Server shut down gracefully');
    process.exit(0);
  });
});
```

