## API Surface Summary

| Endpoint/Operation | Auth Required | Public | Sensitivity | Rate Limited |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `GET /health` | No | Yes | Low | No |
| `GET /users` | No | Yes | **High** (PII) | No |

